       the two involved, to co-opt the empirical strength of the other
       discipline to prop-up its own narrative.
       In this case, the Vox team is using a very small portion of Brash‚Äôs
       work to add a veneer of scientific respectability to their
       argument. As the author here explores, Vox‚Äôs team either were
       ignorant of Brash‚Äôs broader argument or simply choose to ignore the
